0\00\00\00\00\05hints\00\00\00\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\0bOracleHints\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\03\ed\00\00\00\02\00\00\03\ea\00\00\00\07\00\00\03\ea\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\0dFixedPoint128\00\00\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\8dPermissionless oracle poke to record a fresh observation.\0a\0aWrites a new oracle observation using the current pool tick and liquidity.\0aIf called within `MIN_OBSERVATION_INTERVAL` of the last write, this is a no-op.\0a\0aReturns a tuple `(updated, last_timestamp)` where:\0a- `updated` is true if a new observation was recorded\0a- `last_timestamp` is the timestamp of the latest observation after this call\00\00\00\00\00\00\0bpoke_oracle\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\10oracle_slot_hint\00\00\00\0a\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\03\ed\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\06\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\01hReturns oracle hints for deterministic queries.\0a\0aConvenience function that returns both slot and checkpoint hints\0ain a single call, ready to pass to swap/mint/burn/observe functions.\0a\0aWorks both before and after pool initialization:\0a- Before init: returns `{ slot: computed, checkpoint: 0 }`\0a- After init: returns `{ slot: computed, checkpoint: actual_count }`\00\00\00\10get_oracle_hints\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\0bOracleHints\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\ffGet oracle status for UI decisions.\0a\0aReturns information about the oracle's current state to help the frontend\0adecide when to show/enable the \22Refresh price\22 button.\0a\0a# Returns\0aA tuple `(last_timestamp, age_seconds, can_poke)` where:\0a- `last_timestamp`: Unix timestamp of the most recent observation\0a- `age_seconds`: How many seconds have elapsed since the last observation\0a- `can_poke`: Whether calling `poke_oracle` would update the oracle\0a(respects MIN_OBSERVATION_INTERVAL - at least 1 ledger \e2\89\88 5 seconds)\00\00\00\00\11get_oracle_status\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\03\ed\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\06\00\00\00\06\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\dcMints liquidity to a position.\0a\0aCreates or adds to a liquidity position in the specified tick range.\0aTransfers the required amounts of both tokens from the sender.\0a\0a# Arguments\0a* `env` - The contract environment\0a* `sender` - Address initiating the mint and providing tokens (requires auth)\0a* `recipient` - Address receiving the liquidity position (position owner)\0a* `tick_lower` - Lower tick of the position range\0a* `tick_upper` - Upper tick of the position range\0a* `amount` - Amount of liquidity to mint\0a\0a# Returns\0a* `Ok((amount0, amount1))` - Amounts of tokens deposited\0a* `Err(AmountShouldBeGreaterThanZero)` if amount is zero\0a* `Err(Locked)` if pool is currently locked\0a* `Err(InsufficientToken0/Token1)` if token transfer fails\00\00\00\04mint\00\00\00\06\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06sender\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\09recipient\00\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0atick_lower\00\00\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0atick_upper\00\00\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06amount\00\00\00\00\00\0a\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\05hints\00\00\00\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\0bOracleHints\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\03\ed\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\0a\00\00\00\0a\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\d2Returns a tick bitmap word (public variant).\0a\0a# Arguments\0a* `env` - The contract environment\0a* `word_pos` - The word position in the bitmap\0a\0a# Returns\0a256-bit word from the tick bitmap, or zero if uninitialized\00\00\00\00\00\16get_tick_bitmap_public\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\08word_pos\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\0c\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\09Quotes an exact input swap without executing it.\0a\0aSimulates a swap to determine output amount and final price without\0atransferring tokens or modifying state.\0a\0a# Arguments\0a* `env` - The contract environment\0a* `zero_for_one` - True if swapping token0 for token1, false otherwise\0a* `amount_in` - Exact amount of input tokens\0a* `sqrt_price_limit_x96` - Price limit for the swap in Q64.96 format\0a\0a# Returns\0a* `Ok(SwapResult)` containing output amount and final sqrt price\0a* `Err` if swap would fail (invalid price limit, etc.)\00\00\00\00\00\00\11quote_exact_input\00\00\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0czero_for_one\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\09amount_in\00\00\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\14sqrt_price_limit_x96\00\00\00\0c\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\0aSwapResult\00\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\02;Quotes an exact output swap without executing it.\0a\0aSimulates a swap to determine input amount required for a desired output\0awithout transferring tokens or modifying state.\0a\0a# Arguments\0a* `env` - The contract environment\0a* `zero_for_one` - True if swapping token0 for token1, false otherwise\0a* `amount_out` - Exact amount of output tokens desired\0a* `sqrt_price_limit_x96` - Price limit for the swap in Q64.96 format\0a\0a# Returns\0a* `Ok(SwapResult)` containing required input amount and final sqrt price\0a* `Err` if swap would fail (invalid price limit, insufficient liquidity)\00\00\00\00\12quote_exact_output\00\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0czero_for_one\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0aamount_out\00\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\14sqrt_price_limit_x96\00\00\00\0c\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\0aSwapResult\00\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\01qReturns position data for a specific owner and tick range.\0a\0a# Arguments\0a* `env` - The contract environment\0a* `recipient` - Address of the position owner\0a* `tick_lower` - Lower tick of the position range\0a* `tick_upper` - Upper tick of the position range\0a\0a# Returns\0aPositionData containing liquidity, fee growth, and tokens owed\0a\0a# Panics\0aPanics if position doesn't exist\00\00\00\00\00\00\09positions\00\00\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\09recipient\00\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0atick_lower\00\00\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0atick